@using Microsoft.AspNetCore.Identity
@using CineVerify.Models
@inject SignInManager<ApplicationUser> SignInManager
@inject UserManager<ApplicationUser> UserManager

<ul class="navbar-nav">
    @if (SignInManager.IsSignedIn(User))
    {
        <li class="nav-item">
            <a class="nav-link text-dark" asp-page="/Manage/Index" title="Manage">
                Ciao @(User.Identity?.Name?.Split('@')[0])!
            </a>
        </li>
        <li class="nav-item">
            <form class="form-inline" asp-page="/Logout" method="post">
                <button type="submit" class="nav-link btn btn-link text-dark">Logout</button>
            </form>
        </li>
    }
    else
    {
        <li class="nav-item">
            <a class="nav-link text-dark" asp-page="/Register">Registrati</a>
        </li>
        <li class="nav-item">
            <a class="nav-link text-dark" asp-page="/Login">Login</a>
        </li>
    }
</ul>